  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为RTLAmba库设计一个整体架构图，展示它的四大功能模块。核心接口层要包含AXI4、AXI4-Lite、APB和AXI-Stream这四种总线协议。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RTLAmba",
        "Core",
        "AXI4",
        "AXIL4",
        "APB",
        "AXIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。AXI4是完整的全功能版本，AXIL4是简化版，APB是低功耗总线，AXIS是流式传输。这四种都要支持Master和Slave模式吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXI4",
        "AXIL4",
        "APB",
        "AXIS",
        "Master",
        "Slave"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，AXI4和AXIL4都需要Master/Slave，APB还要额外支持Crossbar，AXIS也是Master/Slave。另外AXI4要标注Full以区分Lite版本。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXI4",
        "AXIL4",
        "APB",
        "AXIS",
        "Master",
        "Slave",
        "Crossbar"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Core子图已经画好，四种接口都按你的要求标注了。接下来是Monitor部分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "AXI4",
        "AXIL4",
        "APB",
        "AXIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Monitor Infrastructure这块需要四层结构。最底层是axi_monitor_base，作为所有监控器的基类。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Monitor",
        "MON_BASE",
        "axi_monitor_base"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这个MON_BASE是抽象基类吗？它跟上面四种总线接口是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MON_BASE",
        "AXI4",
        "AXIL4",
        "APB",
        "AXIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "MON_BASE被AXI4、AXIL4、APB这三种接口共享，AXIS暂时不需要监控。然后MON_BASE上面挂Transaction Manager处理事务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MON_BASE",
        "MON_TRANS",
        "AXI4",
        "AXIL4",
        "APB",
        "AXIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加MON_BASE到MON_TRANS的连接。继续往上是Reporter？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MON_BASE",
        "MON_TRANS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，MON_TRANS把数据汇总到MON_REPORT，最后统一输出到Monitor Bus。这个bus是64-bit的packet格式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MON_TRANS",
        "MON_REPORT",
        "MONBUS",
        "64-bit packets"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Monitor子图完成了，四层结构：MON_BASE → MON_TRANS → MON_REPORT → MONBUS。接下来画Infrastructure？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Monitor",
        "MON_BASE",
        "MON_TRANS",
        "MON_REPORT",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "GAXI Infrastructure放FIFO、Skid Buffer和CDC Utilities。FIFO和Skid都要支持同步和异步两种模式。",
